        <abstract>
            <p>The illness and death of his daughter have delayed his answers to CD’s queries. He has, however, worked on the circulation of the eye and has almost finished a paper on it, which he will send to CD. In general, the views of Charles Bell are confirmed.</p>
            <p>As for CD’s second query, he doubts that the relationship exists, but will answer fully in next letter.</p>
        </abstract>
